N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 205.11 - Disbursement of funds

State Regulations

Disbursement of funds shall be made in the manner described
in the rules and regulations promulgated by the commissioner to effectuate the
provisions and intent of the act, and in accordance with the provisions of this
program. Notes
